item.title: Jan & Doe Ferments
item.author: dsborrus@gmail.com (Daniel Scott Borrus)
item.description: Jan & Doe Ferments specializes in crafting delicious and wonderful foods for the Williamsburg community. From our county-famous hot sauces, to our inventive and renowned wines, you are sure to find something that excites your soul. Coming soon to the Williamsburg and York County farmers markets!
